{"tid":395003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登大軍] 大家一齊去中大學生會fb report個班仆街五毛","createTime":"2017-09-10T12:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T08:40:18.000Z","uid":127929,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea60032f029c8aebdaaf686945a9b976092589e","tid":395003,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"每人report幾十個假ac就夠<br />\n記得report 比1星既post同開垃圾post既五毛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/CUHK.SU/reviews/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FCUHK.SU%2Freviews%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=Z33%2F7%2BY5kcTcl6mDTHEi8TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f0d3fa9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/CUHK.SU/reviews/?ref=page_internal</a><br />\n<br />\n支那人憑咩學人上美帝fb呀，仲要係香港人地頭做埋啲咁小學雞既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那留學生咁唔滿意咪唔好黎香港讀書囉，死返大陸飲奶啦屌你仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那人同五毛我屌你老母呀，滾出香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就report左十幾個，雖然班支那人既行為好幼稚，對方人多但咁唔代表佢地有權係香港人既地頭搞事，大家report 得幾多就幾多，積少成多總有啲用既，好過乜都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/202355_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F202355_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d2cbab4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/202359_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F202359_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e90f7944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/202403_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F202403_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=896f997e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各位巴絲，就算失望，不能絕望，快啲幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\nbtw, 話不了/冇用/唔關自己事個堆人我祝你全家生愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a9c18a088738cb165ae3a23a2adf0cd91decc6","tid":395003,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fbdfe57642ab5c7afedc5bc7f7cd40c4bec846","tid":395003,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"我都會做,但係我可以話你聽,facebook唔會做嘢. 班垃圾而家最叻就係滅聲"},{"pid":"0fef4d25c101d9a75f41ef15138f654d0b0a7cdb","tid":395003,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都會做,但係我可以話你聽,facebook唔會做嘢. 班垃圾而家最叻就係滅聲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/213151_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F213151_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c3ee1890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/213238_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F213238_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bfc219d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗一個鐘就得，加油呀大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e3a21a87f59472e245384579ea2be593d918d9","tid":395003,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"各位巴打 想一嘗屠殺支那人的滋味嗎？現在有機會了<br />\n<a href=\"https://l